title: Phish - 1990/06/16:  Townshend Family Park - Townshend, VT  [SBD
description:
This is from bt.etree.org, properly tagged (I use Jaikoz).  A classic three-set show, the last from summer 1990.


Saturday, 06/16/1990 

Townshend Family Park, Townshend, VT

Soundcheck: Carolina, Funky Bitch

Set 1: AC/DC Bag > Divided Sky > Wilson, Reba, Horn, Uncle Pen > Bouncing Around the Room, Timber (Jerry) > Lawn Boy > Possum

Set 2: Golgi Apparatus, Esther > Tweezer, My Sweet One > Bathtub Gin, You Enjoy Myself > The Lizards, Run Like an Antelope

Set 3: La Grange, Ya Mar[1], Foam, The Oh Kee Pa Ceremony > Suzy Greenberg, Fee, Rocky Top, Caravan > Hold Your Head Up > If I Only Had a Brain > Hold Your Head Up > Mike's Song > I Am Hydrogen > Weekapaug Groove

Encore: Contact > Big Black Furry Creature from Mars

Encore 2: Good Times Bad Times

[1] Mike played Happy Birthday in the beginning.
